{
  "texts": [
    "Different from [48], we do not add learnable parameters in our heuristic landmark shifting module and instead construct a learnable cooccurrence scoring module (Sec.",
    "D.2.3) that effectively facilitates cooccurrence-based correctable landmark discovery.",
    "Moreover, we conduct fine-grained shifting among landmarks rather than sub-instructions to enable sequential landmark discovery.",
    "D.2.2 Landmark DiscoveryIn discrete VLN task, the actions are chosen from candidate single-view observations.",
    "Therefore, to adapt our landmark discovery framework for navigation action prediction, we transform the landmark discovery as locating the landmark in one of the candidate observations, which is consistent with the action prediction process."
  ]
}